author: ryan
msg: SOLR-1377:  The TokenizerFactory API has changed to explicitly return a Tokenizer
rather then a TokenStream (that may be or may not be a Tokenizer).  This change
is required to take advantage of the Token reuse improvements in lucene 2.9.

author: dag
msg: DERBY-4208 Parameters ? with OFFSET and/or FETCH
This patch implements the use of dynamic parameters with OFFSET/FETCH and adds new tests.
